        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Home Educators are Teachers Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill expands the tax deduction for certain expenses of elementary and secondary school teachers to include home school teachers and home schooling expenses.</p>]]>
        </text>
